.P
Each graph has a limited number of IDs:
.P
\fBgraph_0\fP up to 8 IDs.
.br
\fBgraph_1\fP up to 6 IDs.
.br
\fBgraph_2\fP up to 6 IDs.
.P
The following is a configuration example of selected IDs:
.P
