coretemp-isa-0001
.br
Adapter: ISA adapter
.br
Core 1:       +49.0°C  (high = +78.0°C, crit = +100.0°C)  
.br
.P
f71882fg-isa-0a00
.br
Adapter: ISA adapter
.br
3.3V:        +3.30 V
.br
Vcore:       +1.21 V  (max =  +2.04 V)   
.br
Vdimm:       +1.82 V
.br
Vchip:       +1.38 V
